data.text: @taradublinrocks @BarnsCourtney @WonderBallroom Bummer. To cheer you up, you should go see @parcelsmusic at the Roseland tonight!

@taradublinrocks @BarnsCourtney @WonderBallroom Love the Wonder ballroom. Remember seeing Travis there back in 2008-ish… Have you ever been to the Kennedy School? Used to live right across the street. Miss the soaking pool… miss PDX period!!!
